			<h1 id="firstHeading" class="firstHeading" lang="en"><span dir="auto">Water Shader Tutorial</span></h1>
			<div id="bodyContent">
				<div id="contentSub"><div id="mw-revision-info">Revision as of 14:22, 8 June 2015 by <a href="/index.php?title=User:Pixelsmash&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new mw-userlink" title="User:Pixelsmash (page does not exist)">Pixelsmash</a>  <span class="mw-usertoollinks">(<a href="/index.php?title=User_talk:Pixelsmash&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="User talk:Pixelsmash (page does not exist)">Talk</a> | <a href="/Special:Contributions/Pixelsmash" title="Special:Contributions/Pixelsmash">contribs</a>)</span></div><br />
				<div id="mw-revision-nav">(<a href="/index.php?title=Water_Shader_Tutorial&amp;diff=prev&amp;oldid=14488" title="Water Shader Tutorial">diff</a>) <a href="/index.php?title=Water_Shader_Tutorial&amp;direction=prev&amp;oldid=14488" title="Water Shader Tutorial">← Older revision</a> | Latest revision (diff) | Newer revision → (diff)</div></div>
																<div id="mw-content-text" lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr"><div id="toc" class="toc"><div id="toctitle"><h2>Contents</h2></div>
